column3: str

<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Annine is beside herself with worry for her missing brothers.
Search for the stocky miner.
Search for the stout miner.
Report to the stocky miner.
Could I ask a favor?
My two brothers set out for Mount Biran Mines to see if there's anything worth salvaging, but they've been gone an awfully long time.

Would you be able to go and look for them? I'd go myself, but I hear the place is crawling with all sorts of nasty creatures, and fighting's not my forte. I don't expect you to do it for free, of course.
One of them is a bit of a big lad, and the other is also quite big, but slightly less so. I'm sure you'll know them when you see them.
Eh? Who are you?
She was bloody right when she said it was dangerous here.
We ran into a pack of coyotes, and we were separated when we tried to outrun them.
I got away but I don't know what's happened to my brother.
Hopefully, he found somewhere to hide. Will you help me look for him?
I'll join you in the search once I've caught my breath. I don't think I've ever run so fast in my life!
Annine sent you to find us? Thanks, stranger. I'd better go and see if my brother is all right.
I was afraid we'd never get out of here alive!
I never thought I'd be so happy to see him!
Now that we've got reinforcements, we should be able to carry on where we left off. It'll be a lot easier with someone to cover our backs.
Hold on now, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>she<Else/>he</If> didn't come here for that.
Before we get ahead of ourselves, let me give you this. It's the least we can offer you for coming to our rescue.
